    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>温馨提示：三思而后行，切忌在未理解指令具体含义之前直接复制粘贴！！！      </p><h3 id="1-下载镜像，制作安装U盘，使用U盘启动（具体步骤略）"><a href="#1-下载镜像，制作安装U盘，使用U盘启动（具体步骤略）" class="headerlink" title="1.下载镜像，制作安装U盘，使用U盘启动（具体步骤略）"></a>1.下载镜像，制作安装U盘，使用U盘启动（具体步骤略）</h3><p>贴上下载页面地址<br><a href="https://archlinux.org/download/">https://archlinux.org/download/</a></p><h3 id="2-启动后，首先连接网络"><a href="#2-启动后，首先连接网络" class="headerlink" title="2.启动后，首先连接网络"></a>2.启动后，首先连接网络</h3><p>使用WiFi连接互联网:  </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">iwctl device list</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 将DEVICE换成你的网络设备</span></span><br><span class="line">iwctl station DEVICE scan</span><br><span class="line">iwctl station DEVICE get-network</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果有密码(将PASSWORD换成密码，将DEVICE换成你的网络设备，将NETWORK换成你要用的网络)</span></span><br><span class="line">iwctl --passphrase PASSWORD station DEVICE connect NETWORK</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 如果没有密码</span></span><br><span class="line">iwctl DEVICE connect NETWORK</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或直接使用网线连接互联网  </p><p>对连接情况进行测试</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ping www.baidu.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-同步网络时间"><a href="#3-同步网络时间" class="headerlink" title="3.同步网络时间"></a>3.同步网络时间</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">timedatectl set-ntp <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-修改发行源"><a href="#4-修改发行源" class="headerlink" title="4.修改发行源"></a>4.修改发行源</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>不想用vim的话，用nano也可以<br>推荐把163源放到最前面，其他的国内源也可以，建议多写几行，然后把国外源全删掉<br>具体换源方法参照各大开源镜像站的介绍</p><h3 id="5-磁盘分区"><a href="#5-磁盘分区" class="headerlink" title="5.磁盘分区"></a>5.磁盘分区</h3><p>使用以下命令查看磁盘</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lsblk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>或者</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fdisk -l</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用以下命令进行系统分区</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fdisk /dev/XXX  <span class="comment">#XXX换成你要指定的磁盘</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>不想用fdisk的话，用cfdisk也可以。修改完记得写入保存。<br>将要分3个区：ESP，根，交换。如果你想使用交换文件，交换分区可以不要。你也可以分一个home区，看你是否需要了。<br>一般来说，ESP几百MB完全足够，根分区推荐给大一点（一般来说一百多G够日常使用，有别的需求可以更多），swap分区的大小建议与你的运行内存大小一致。<br>如果你没有ESP，那就需要新建。注意！如果你已经有ESP，那么里面很可能有其他系统的引导文件，下面的格式化（mkfs）步骤一定要慎重！<br>为了方便描述，现在规定：<br>ESP是/dev/sda1<br>根是/dev/sda2<br>swap是/dev/sda3<br>在接下来的安装过程中，请结合自己实际情况修改<br>格式化ESP：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkfs.vfat /dev/sda1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>格式化根分区：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda2      <span class="comment">#也可以是其他的文件系统</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设置交换分区：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkswap /dev/sda3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启用交换分区：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">swapon /dev/sda3</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-挂载分区"><a href="#6-挂载分区" class="headerlink" title="6.挂载分区"></a>6.挂载分区</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mount /dev/sda2 /mnt</span><br><span class="line">mkdir -p /mnt/boot/EFI</span><br><span class="line">mount /dev/sda1 /mnt/boot/EFI</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使用</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lsblk</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>可以检查分区挂载是否正确  </p><h3 id="7-安装系统软件包"><a href="#7-安装系统软件包" class="headerlink" title="7.安装系统软件包"></a>7.安装系统软件包</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacstrap -i /mnt base base-devel linux linux-firmware linux-headers dhcpcd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>推荐一并安装：networkmanager ，ntfs-3g  </p><h3 id="8-配置fstab"><a href="#8-配置fstab" class="headerlink" title="8.配置fstab"></a>8.配置fstab</h3><p>自动配置：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">genfstab -U /mnt &gt;&gt; /mnt/etc/fstab      <span class="comment">#也可以是genfstab -L /mnt &gt;&gt; /mnt/etc/fstab</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>手动配置请自行查阅archwiki。<br>使用</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cat /mnt/etc/fstab</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>检查 fstab 是否正确  </p><h3 id="9-切换至新系统"><a href="#9-切换至新系统" class="headerlink" title="9.切换至新系统"></a>9.切换至新系统</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">arch-chroot /mnt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="10-修改-locale-设定"><a href="#10-修改-locale-设定" class="headerlink" title="10.修改 locale 设定"></a>10.修改 locale 设定</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S nano vim</span><br><span class="line">vim /etc/locale.gen      <span class="comment">#也可以用nano</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>找到下面这两行</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#en_US.UTF8 UTF-8</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#zh_CN.UTF8 UTF-8</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>反注释即可<br>接下来</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">locale-gen</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">echo</span> LANG=en_US.UTF-8 &gt; /etc/locale.conf</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="11-时间设置"><a href="#11-时间设置" class="headerlink" title="11.时间设置"></a>11.时间设置</h3><p>设置时区</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ln -sf /usr/share/zoneinfo/Asia/Shanghai /etc/localtime</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>假如你在别的时区，也可以设成你所在的时区<br>同步硬件时间</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hwclock --systohc --utc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="12-安装启动引导"><a href="#12-安装启动引导" class="headerlink" title="12.安装启动引导"></a>12.安装启动引导</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S dosfstools grub efibootmgr os-prober</span><br><span class="line">grub-install --target=x86_64-efi --efi-directory=/boot/EFI --recheck</span><br><span class="line">grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="13-修改-root-密码"><a href="#13-修改-root-密码" class="headerlink" title="13.修改 root 密码"></a>13.修改 root 密码</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">passwd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="14-创建新用户"><a href="#14-创建新用户" class="headerlink" title="14.创建新用户"></a>14.创建新用户</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">useradd -m -g users -s /bin/bash YOURS_USERNAME      <span class="comment">#将YOURS_USERNAME替换成你的用户名</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改密码</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">passwd YOURS_USERNAME      <span class="comment">#将YOURS_USERNAME替换成你的用户名</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>给新用户 sudo 权限</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vim /etc/sudoers</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>参照其中的这段代码</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">root ALL=(ALL) ALL</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>添加</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">YOURS_USERNAME ALL=(ALL) ALL      <span class="comment">#将YOURS_USERNAME替换成你的用户名</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="15-安装WiFi控制器（如果你需要）"><a href="#15-安装WiFi控制器（如果你需要）" class="headerlink" title="15.安装WiFi控制器（如果你需要）"></a>15.安装WiFi控制器（如果你需要）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S iw wpa_supplicant dialog</span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> dhcpcd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="16-安装显卡驱动"><a href="#16-安装显卡驱动" class="headerlink" title="16.安装显卡驱动"></a>16.安装显卡驱动</h3><p>Intel 显卡安装</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S xf86-video-intel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>NVIDIA显卡安装  </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S xf86-video-nouveau</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>AMD显卡安装  </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S xf86-video-ati</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>另外，接下来要安装的xorg全家桶里包含了通用驱动。<br>还有，xf86-video-intel可能会导致闪屏、花屏，假如你遇到了这些现象，请改用xorg的通用驱动（xf86-video-vesa）。         </p><h3 id="17-安装xorg"><a href="#17-安装xorg" class="headerlink" title="17.安装xorg"></a>17.安装xorg</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S xorg</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="18-安装一些中文字体"><a href="#18-安装一些中文字体" class="headerlink" title="18.安装一些中文字体"></a>18.安装一些中文字体</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S ttf-dejavu wqy-microhei</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="19-安装桌面环境"><a href="#19-安装桌面环境" class="headerlink" title="19.安装桌面环境"></a>19.安装桌面环境</h3><p>假如你要用xfce</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S xfce4 xfce4-goodies</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> lightdm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>假如你要用KDE</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S plasma kde-applications</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> sddm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>假如你要用Gnome</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S gnome gnome-extra</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> gdm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>假如你要用DDE</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S deepin deepin-extra</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> lightdm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>假如你要用其他的DE或者WM，请自行查阅archwiki。  </p><h3 id="20-安装networkmanager（假如之前未安装）"><a href="#20-安装networkmanager（假如之前未安装）" class="headerlink" title="20.安装networkmanager（假如之前未安装）"></a>20.安装networkmanager（假如之前未安装）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S networkmanager</span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> NetworkManager</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意，即使你已经安装了networkmanager，你也应该执行以下指令</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> NetworkManager</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="21-安装触控板驱动（假如需要）"><a href="#21-安装触控板驱动（假如需要）" class="headerlink" title="21.安装触控板驱动（假如需要）"></a>21.安装触控板驱动（假如需要）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S xf86-input-synaptics</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="22-安装蓝牙驱动（假如需要）"><a href="#22-安装蓝牙驱动（假如需要）" class="headerlink" title="22.安装蓝牙驱动（假如需要）"></a>22.安装蓝牙驱动（假如需要）</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pacman -S bluez bluez-utils</span><br><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> bluetooth.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="23-退出chroot"><a href="#23-退出chroot" class="headerlink" title="23.退出chroot"></a>23.退出chroot</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">exit</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="24-重启"><a href="#24-重启" class="headerlink" title="24.重启"></a>24.重启</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">reboot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="25-enjoy！"><a href="#25-enjoy！" class="headerlink" title="25.enjoy！"></a>25.enjoy！</h3>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
